title: Beyond Mombasa [1956 - UK] (Cornel Wilde) Kenya adventure
description:
Beyond Mombasa (1956 - UK, USA)

Action / Adventure / Mystery

starring . . . . Cornel Wilde, Donna Reed, Leo Genn, Christopher Lee
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0049005/


Most of the film was photographed in the Coast Province of Kenya

An expedition goes into the African veldt to solve the mystery of the death of an explorer who had discovered a valuable uranium mine. A good deal of African fauna and flora is observed en route, and the picture is photographed in colour so that it captures and entertains the eye. With a stellar cast featuring Cornel Wilde, Donna Reed and Christopher Lee, the exotic locales and animal attacks aren't the only pleasures in this jungle tale.
